sections.heading: therapy assistant; supervision required
sections.text: An occupational therapy assistant may deliver occupational therapy services enumerated in section 38-2510 in collaboration with and under the supervision of an occupational therapist.SourceLaws 2004, LB 1005, ยง 125;R.S.Supp.,2006, ยง 71-6119;Laws 2007, LB463, ยง
